{"tid":1812614,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"新年前節目, 和你行年宵, 大家傾下幾時一齊去行啦","createTime":"2020-01-05T15:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T14:18:55.000Z","uid":76310,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8060b06c9c4c3c753626623e45870cf59606ea50","tid":1812614,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"農曆年宵市場地點和日期<br />\n2020年農曆年宵市場將於2020年1月19日至2020年農曆年初一清晨(即2020年1月25日)舉行，為期七天，地點如下:<br />\n銅鑼灣維多利亞公園(銅鑼灣)<br />\n東涌達東路花園(東涌)<br />\n深水埗花墟公園(旺角)<br />\n深水埗長沙灣遊樂場(長沙灣)<br />\n黃大仙摩士公園(黃大仙)<br />\n觀塘觀塘遊樂場(觀塘)<br />\n葵青葵涌運動場(葵涌)<br />\n荃灣沙咀道遊樂場(荃灣)<br />\n屯門天后廟廣場(屯門)<br />\n元朗東頭工業區遊樂場(元朗)<br />\n北區石湖墟遊樂場(上水)<br />\n大埔天后宮風水廣場(大埔)<br />\n沙田源禾遊樂場(沙田)<br />\n西貢萬宜遊樂場(西貢)<br />\n將軍澳寶康公園(將軍澳)<br />\n<br />\n新年前節目, 和你行年宵, 大家傾下幾時一齊去行啦<br />\n而家傾定好細節, 差不多啦<br />\n宣傳叫人一齊去和你行年宵, 都需要時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef5f41eff3c61e4c0b850b48f78c6c2cb51cfde","tid":1812614,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727609ef17e37bab14a2b1b6b169e796765e8427","tid":1812614,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"咁多年宵市場, 大家覺得集中幾區<br />\n定真係分晒咁多區去和你SHOP<br />\n時間應該係放工後/六日"},{"pid":"fccc3064a82ea0d045c9fa6fb9b15b8cf7b87a04","tid":1812614,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a239295c7fe17812d67df75fd3200a47c5ed2dc2","tid":1812614,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gi